  • It's time for a new kawaii hoodie!

    This cute hoodie is sure to give your look a kawaii edge. Featuring Bubu the Chilling Bunny lying on its oversized pillow reading a book printed on the front of the hoodie. Perfect for wearing around the house or while you're out and about with friends.

    Choose between 12 different colors. We always recommend choosing 1 size up giving you the oversized hoodie look.

    Get ready to give your look a kawaii-style with this hoodie!

    Everyone will fall in love with this hoodie! Made from premium polyester - it feels soft and smooth on the skin for all-day comfort, and the kawaii design will certainly get you noticed. 

    Available in 7 different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below.


    Size (inches) XS S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 38 41 43 45 48 50 52
    Length 24 25 26 27 28 30 31
    Sleeve 21 22 23 23 24 25 26
                   
    Size (cm) XS S M L XL XXL XXXL

    If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com.


    Features

    😍 Made from premium polyester
    😍 Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability
    😍 Kiki's Delivery Service Black Cat On Magical Broomstick on the front

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.


  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
